INSERT INTO `galleries` VALUES (1,'Les 18èmes Journées Internationales de la Biotechnologie','2019-12-31','2020-01-31','<p>C\'est un grand plaisir d\'annoncer les 18&egrave;mes Journ&eacute;es Internationales de la Biotechnologie &raquo;(IDB2019) de l\'Association Tunisienne de Biotechnologie (ATBiotech.) Qui se tiendront du 18 au 21 d&eacute;cembre 2019, Marhaba Palace Hotel (5 &eacute;toiles), El Kantaoui Sousse , Tunisie.</p>\r\n<p>Le comit&eacute; d\'organisation souhaite souligner les points suivants:</p>\r\n<p>Langue: Les pr&eacute;sentations orales pourraient &ecirc;tre en fran&ccedil;ais ou en anglais; pourtant:</p>\r\n<p>- Le r&eacute;sum&eacute; (sans graphisme) doit &ecirc;tre obligatoire en anglais suivant le mod&egrave;le sur le site web.</p>\r\n<p>- Les r&eacute;sum&eacute;s non conformes seront syst&eacute;matiquement rejet&eacute;s.</p>\r\n<p>- Les supports: la pr&eacute;sentation PowerPoint (PPT) et les posters doivent &ecirc;tre en anglais.</p>','الأيام الدولية الثامنة عشر للتكنولوجيا الحيوية','The 18th International Days of Biotechnology','<p style=\"text-align: right;\">إنه لمن دواعي سرورنا أن أعلن اليوم العالمي الثامن عشر للتكنولوجيا الحيوية &raquo;(IDB2019) للجمعية التونسية للتقنية الحيوية (ATBiotech) التي ستعقد يومي 18 و 21 ديسمبر 2019 ، فندق قصر مرحبا (5 نجوم) ، القنطاوي سوسة تونس</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">تود اللجنة المنظمة تسليط الضوء على النقاط التالية:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">اللغة: يمكن أن تكون العروض التقديمية الشفوية باللغة الفرنسية أو الإنجليزية ؛ ومع ذلك:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">- يجب أن يكون الملخص (بدون الرسومات) إلزاميًا باللغة الإنجليزية باتباع النموذج الموجود على موقع الويب.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">- سيتم رفض الملخصات غير المطابقة بشكل منهجي.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">- مواد الدعم: يجب أن يكون العرض التقديمي Power Point (PPT) والملصقات باللغة الإنجليزية.</p>','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Ubuntu, Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #2e2e2e; background-color: #fcfcfc; text-align: justify !important;\">It&rsquo;s a big pleasure to announce the 18<sup>th&nbsp;</sup>International Days of Biotechnology&nbsp;&raquo;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">(IDB2019)&nbsp;</span>of the Tunisian Association of Biotechnology (A.T.Biotech.) that will be held on December, 18<sup>th&nbsp;</sup>&ndash; 21<sup>st&nbsp;</sup>2019<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">,</span>&nbsp;Marhaba Palace Hotel (5 stars), El Kantaoui Sousse, Tunisia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Ubuntu, Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #2e2e2e; background-color: #fcfcfc; text-align: justify !important;\">The organizing committee would like to highlight the following points:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Ubuntu, Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside none; color: #2e2e2e; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">\r\n<li style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none !important; margin: 0px 0px 3px !important 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Language:&nbsp;</span>Oral presentations could be in French or in English; however:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Ubuntu, Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #2e2e2e; background-color: #fcfcfc; text-align: justify !important;\">&ndash; The abstract (without graphics) should be obligatory in English following the model on the web site.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Ubuntu, Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #2e2e2e; background-color: #fcfcfc; text-align: justify !important;\">&ndash; Non-conform abstracts will be systematically rejected.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Ubuntu, Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #2e2e2e; background-color: #fcfcfc; text-align: justify !important;\">&ndash; The support materials: Power point presentation (PPT) and posters&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">should be in English.</span></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'PUBLISHED','les-18emes-journees-internationales-de-la-biotechnologie-3',0,NULL,'2019-09-17 08:10:54','2020-01-14 06:52:39','[]','[]','actualites/16142281_1243484052372903_4507834856531015524_n.jpg','photos','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(2,